The paper deals with recommending investors for crowdfunding projects, which involves analyzing pledging behavior and translating the findings into different recommendation strategies. This suggests that the paper could fall under the sub-categories of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Cybernetics (cs.CY), Social and Behavioral Sciences (cs.SOC), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC).
